title: Otter with white head
creator: The Spanish Bloom
description: Small otter plushie with a white head and a brown body. Fun fact: Otters grey like humans as they age, so otters with white or silver fur at their head are older in age.
subject: Otter
image_alt_text: Small otter plushie with a white head and a brown body

title: Duckie with frog hat
creator: The Spanish Bloom
description: Small duck plushie wearing a green frog hat. Fun fact: Ducklings are yellow because the color helps them blend in with grass and vegetation, hiding them from predators.
subject: Duck
image_alt_text: Small duck plushie wearing a green frog hat.

title: Two-headed cow with star eyes
creator: Cow Abduction Crochet
description: A large cow plushie with two heads and four eyes. Its eyes have silver stars on them, and there is a miniature cow bell around its neck. Fun fact: This plushie design is based on the poem "Two-Headed Calf", by Laura Gilpin.
subject: Cow
image_alt_text: A large cow plushie with two heads and four eyes. Its eyes have silver stars on them, and there is a miniature cow bell around its neck.

title: Colorful mushrooms
creator: Blue Jay Crochet
description: Two small mushroom plushies with eyes, one is purple (left) and the other is blue (right). Fun fact: These plushies are designed after the Lobster Mushroom which are typically orange in color and taste faintly of lobster when cooked.
subject: Mushroom
image_alt_text: Two small mushroom plushies with eyes, one is purple (left) and the other is blue (right).
